parameters: \TA[1]Now, let's begin the second magical girl meeting!

\TA[1]We're going to talk about what we couldn't discuss
yesterday. What is the topic?

\TA[1]I think you, who have been away from the active duty for a
long time, probably don't understand well, but...

\TA[1]There's one method that has been a hot topic among magical
girls recently, meow. And that is...
\TA[1]Ah, are you talking about that video site?

\TA[1]The magical network recording site that was realized with
the technology of this world. It is a different dimension
from real video sites, and it completely protects the
privacy of individuals who are filmed in this important
modern society with mosaic technology.

\TA[1]Furthermore, with the addition of adjustments by magical
girls themselves on the site, it has become relatively easy
to secure high-quality videos that are less affected by the
equipment of the cameraperson. It can be said that it is at
the center of the trends of this era, which has entered the
heyday of streaming.

\TA[1]Yes, that's enough. Sherbet-chan, summarize it in three
lines.

\TA[1]This amazing video site... you can become famous by
uploading videos. Woohoo!
\TA[1]Thanks to the support of the citizens, we won earlier too.

\TA[1]You can think of it as receiving it from many people through
the internet, meow.
\TA[1]Oh, the kids these days are different, huh~.

\TA[1]Huh? Well then, if it's just the two of them, they should
be able to do it without me helping, right?

\TA[1]The privacy policy of DufTube seems to be strict. We are
unable to create an account.
\TA[1]I don't have money to buy equipment.

\TA[1]But Levantia is an adult! They can stream as much as they
want!

\TA[1]In addition, because the disparity here is intense, it's
difficult to stand out.

\TA[1](So, that means they can see me fighting, right?) (...It
might be a little embarrassing.)
\TA[1](But, the fact that I can become stronger is attractive.)

\TA[1](It seems like the villains are getting stronger and
stronger.)
\TA[1]So, how do you do this streaming thing?

\TA[1]I don't understand difficult things because I'm a cat,
meow~.

\TA[1]But Levantia-san is an adult! They have lots of
acquaintances and friends, right?
\TA[1]Huh!? Ah, well, yeah. There are about 100 people.

\TA[1]Surely there must be at least one person among them who
knows about streaming, right?
